headline: Three Reasons Why We Love Yum! Brands (YUM)
summary: Yum! Brands has shown little upside over the past six months. It has held steady at $135 per share, posting a small 1% loss. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500 index’s 14.8% return during that time.
